E%3Cli%3EAn%20AI%20analyst%20said%20plumbers%20and%20electricians'%20jobs%20are%20safe%2C%20but%20%26quot%3BAI%20will%20impact%20any%20job%20that%20has%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20computer%20workers%20will%20likely%20need%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20work%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20newest%20model%20and%20others%20like%20it%20could%20dramatically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchat-gpt4o-not-killing-jobs-teaching-translation-customer-service-experts-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereinvent%20the%20workplace%20wheel.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt4o-launch-ai-new-best-friend-sam-altman-chatgpt-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-4o%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20newest%20multimodal%20model%2C%20can%20input%20and%20output%20a%20combination%20of%20text%2C%20audio%2C%20and%20images.%20The%20technology%20represents%20a%20major%20advancement%20of%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20of%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20announced%20the%20model%20in%20a%20series%20of%20demo%20videos%20on%20Monday%2C%20showcasing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-most-impressive-gpt-4o-demo-videos-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechnology's%20improved%20vision%20and%20voice%20abilities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20videos%20elicited%20both%20wonder%20and%20mockery%2C%20with%20people%20quickly%20making%20comparisons%20to%20the%202013%20sci-fi%20movie%20%26quot%3BHer%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-openai-chatgpt-flirty-cringe-update-gpt4-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20the%20reveal%20made%20him%20%26quot%3Bcringe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20predict%20how%20exactly%20the%20model%20will%20disrupt%20the%20workforce%2C%20GPT-4o%20and%20other%20multimodal%20models%20will%20inevitably%20change%20the%20way%20we%20work%2C%20said%20Maribel%20Lopez%2C%20an%20AI%20analyst%20and%20founder%20of%20research%20and%20strategy%20consulting%20firm%20Lopez%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concept%20of%20multimodal%20models%20will%20impact%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20industries%20because%20it%20handles%20text%2C%20video%2C%20and%20audio%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20all%20of%20those%20impacts%20will%20necessarily%20be%20negative%2C%20Lopez%20said.%20For%20example%2C%20electricians%2C%20plumbers%2C%20and%20other%20tactile%20workers%20could%20use%20multimodal%20AI%20to%20make%20their%20jobs%20easier%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20workers%20who%20fix%20specialized%20equipment%2C%20AI%20might%20be%20very%20helpful%20in%20troubleshooting%20or%20fixing%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20won't%20replace%20them%20because%20they%20have%20to%20be%20there%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20companies%20are%20working%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcovariant-ai-chatgpt-software-warehouse-robots-work-better-handle-mistakes-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20robots%20that%20can%20do%20physical%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20those%20models%20are%20typically%20better%20suited%20for%20repeated%20menial%20tasks%20like%20welding%20bolts%20than%20complex%20blue-collar%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20other%20industries%20could%20have%20more%20of%20a%20challenge%20adapting%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20multimodal%20AI%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20will%20impact%20any%20job%20that%20has%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20industries%20like%20supply%20chain%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20consensus%20is%20that%20anywhere%20from%2020%25%20to%2030%25%20of%20tasks%20completed%20by%20%26quot%3Bcomputer%20workers%26quot%3B%20will%20eventually%20be%20offset%20by%20AI%2C%20Lopez%20said.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20computer%20workers%20will%20find%20themselves%20unemployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20paralegals%20as%20an%20example%2C%20Lopez%20said%20their%20jobs%20could%20shift%20from%20tracking%20down%20documents%20and%20writing%20up%20summaries%20%E2%80%94%20two%20tasks%20that%20can%20take%20a%20person%20hours%20but%20which%20AI%20can%20complete%20in%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20to%20tasks%20yet%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AI%20challenge%20is%20that%20it%20forces%20all%20of%20us%20to%20enhance%20our%20skillsets%2C%26quot%3B%20Lopez%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20a%20change%20for%20all%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20appears%20that%20OpenAI%20doesn't%20want%20GPT-4o%20to%20feel%20like%20doomsday%20for%20computer%20workers%2C%20either.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20included%20a%20demo%20video%20showing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-4o-real-time-feedback-coding-math-demo-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechnology%20acting%20as%20a%20personal%20assistant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suggesting%20changes%20to%20code%20in%20real%20time%2C%20and%20offering%20a%20one-sentence%20summary%20of%20text.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-4o-ai-model-work-easier-for-electricians-plumbers-openai-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715768941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66440390f27898f532d7ae1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt-4o-ai-model-work-easier-for-electricians-plumbers-openai-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20new%20multimodal%20model%20could%20help%20plumbers%20and%20electricians%20do%20their%20jobs%20more%20effectively%2C%20AI%20analyst%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%