n%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20French%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onisr.securite-routiere.gouv.fr%2Fen%2Froad-safety-performance%2Fannual-road-safety-reports%2F2022-road-safety-annual-report%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPublication%2520on%25204th%2520October%252C%25202023%2C10.3%2525%2520higher%2520than%2520in%25202021.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%203%2C550%20people%20were%20killed%20on%20the%20roads%20in%20mainland%20France%20and%20its%20overseas%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20look%20at%20the%20figures%2C%20they%20are%20clear%3A%20to%20stay%20alive%20behind%20the%20wheel%2C%20the%20best%20thing%20for%20men%20to%20do%20is%20adopt%20the%20same%20behavior%20as%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20campaign's%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVictimes%20%26amp%3B%20Citoyens%20also%20cited%20data%20showing%20that%2088%25%20of%20young%20drivers%20are%20killed%20by%20men%2C%2093%25%20of%20drunk%20drivers%20involved%20in%20accidents%20are%20men%2C%20and%20women%20are%20eight%20times%20less%20likely%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts%20to%20have%20a%20fatal%20accident%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStatistically%2C%20driving%20like%20a%20woman%20means%20only%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20staying%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20awareness%20campaign%20will%20run%20across%20print%2C%20digital%2C%20and%20metro%20platforms%2C%20and%20will%20also%20use%20a%20chatbot%20to%20respond%20to%20posts%20on%20X%20about%20women%20driving.%20according%20to%20the%20campaign's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iihs.org%2Ftopics%2Ffatality-statistics%2Fdetail%2Fmales-and-females%23trends%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsurance%20Institute%20for%20Highway%20Safety%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethe%20number%20of%20male%20crash%20deaths%20was%20more%20than%20twice%20the%20number%20of%20female%20crash%20deat