ms%2C%20and%20massagers.%20I've%20tried%20variations%20of%20those%20things%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20they%20do%20help%20relieve%20pain%20slightly%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20undo%20the%20damage%20done%20by%20sitting%20like%20a%20gargoyle%20on%20my%20couch%20for%20nine%20hours%20every%20day.%20But%20when%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20ad%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1f7a1bc0e8c77d2f4945b27390c8d0d173ea98ac4e2cda03acc6a2d651c1a005%26postID%3D662a6b0ad81bf7a9b9c85bc5%26postSlug%3Dready-rocker-back-pain-work-from-home-posture-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FREADY-ROCKER-Portable-Ergonomic-Rocker%252Fdp%252FB0CMWBXL11%252Fref%253Dasc_df_B0CMWBXL11%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Ready%20Rocker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20way%20it%20worked%20made%20sense%20to%20me%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20device%20that%20changes%20how%20you%20sit%2C%20correcting%20your%20posture%20in%20the%20moment.%20In%20theory%2C%20it%20helps%20prevent%20the%20pain%20rather%20than%20work%20to%20relieve%20it%20after%20you've%20already%20done%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20appealed%20to%20me%20because%20you%20can%20rock%20back%20and%20forth%20a%20bit%20while%20using%20it%2C%20and%20I%20can%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsymptoms-of-adhd-time-to-see-psychologist-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebit%20fidgety%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20it%20pretty%20much%20anywhere%3A%20on%20a%20couch%2C%20chair%2C%20or%20leaning%20against%20the%20headboard%20of%20a%20bed.%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20(Note%3A%20It%20was%20%2498%20when%20I%20purchased%20it%2C%20though%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publish%2C%20this%20color%20is%20on%20sale%20on%20Amazon%20for%20%2489.%20It%20comes%20in%20multiple%20colors.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ready%20Rocker%20sitting%20on%20a%20grey%20couch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a8efdb4abc992e8c6af0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ready%20Rocker%20allows%20the%20user%20to%20work%20from%20a%20couch%20or%20bed%20without%20sacrificing%20good%20posture.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Rosemary%20Donahue%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d33ced4-1118-47d5-8521-ea1f285f21eb%5C%22%3EI've%20had%20it%20for%202%20months%20and%20have%20noticed%20a%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20positions%20depending%20on%20how%20far%20forward%20you%20want%20to%20start%20%26quot%3Brocking%26quot%3B%20from%2C%20and%20you%20just%20press%20the%20two%20buttons%20on%20either%20side%20to%20adjust%20it.%20When%20I%20started%20to%20use%20it%2C%20I%20immediately%20felt%20myself%20sitting%20up%20straighter%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%2C%20I%20noticed%20I%20wasn't%20hunching%20my%20shoulders%20and%20neck%20forward%20nearly%20as%20much%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20main%20issue%20lately.%20It's%20also%20nice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20rock%20slightly%20while%20I%20work%20because%20moving%20a%20little%20helps%20me%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20it%20for%20about%20two%20months%20now%20and%20though%20I%20don't%20use%20it%20all%20day%2C%20I%20do%20use%20it%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20each%20day%2C%20and%20I've%20noticed%20less%20overall%20pain%2C%20especially%20in%20my%20upper%20back%20and%20neck.%20I%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoga-poses-to-relieve-neck-back-shoulder-pain-photos-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20doing%20yoga%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20this%20period%2C%20and%20I%20do%20poses%20that%20are%20targeted%20toward%20those%20areas%2C%20which%20could%20be%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20I'm%20getting%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it's%20the%20Ready%20Rocker%2C%20yoga%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20the%20two%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20continue%20my%20new%20routine%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fready-rocker-back-pain-work-from-home-posture-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715764862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663a8ac79686a6f37bfcfb65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fready-rocker-back-pain-work-from-home-posture-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I'm%20often%20working%20on%20my%20laptop%20and%20sitting%20on%20the%20couch%20much%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20my%20back%20and%20neck%20pain%20has%20worsened.%20Using%20the%20Ready%20Rocker%20has%20helped.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rosemary%20Donahue)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fready-rocker-back-pain-work-from-home-posture-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%20Playoffs%20Chances%20In%20Percentage%3A%20SRH%2087.3%25%2C%20CSK%2072.7%25%2C%20RCB...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20IPL%202024%20Playoffs%20race%20now%20has%20five%20teams%20vying%20for%20two%20available%20slots.%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20and%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20have%20already%20sealed%20two%20spots.%20That%20leaves%20five%20teams%20-%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%2C%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20-%20fighting%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20spots.%20Barring%20SRH%2C%20all%20the%20other%20teams%20have%20only%20one%20match%20remaining.%20It%20means%20that%20net%20run-rates%20will%20most%20probably%20come%20in%20to%20play%20to%20decide%20the%20final%20spot%20for%20the%20IPL%202024%20playoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20IPL%202024's%20official%20broadcasters%20Star%20Sports%2C%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20have%2087.3%20percent%20chance%20to%20qualify.%20It%2