C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Dell%2C%20Chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20Dell%20Technologies.%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20flags%2C%20reflecting%20Dell's%20corporate%20colors%2C%20are%20the%20highest%20rank%20and%20are%20given%20out%20for%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20on-site%20presence%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%2039%20days%20or%20more%20in%20the%20office%20per%20quarter%2C%20while%20green%20flags%20are%20allocated%20for%20%26quot%3Bregular%20onsite%20presence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYellow%20flags%20reflect%20%26quot%3Bsome%20onsite%20presence%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20red%20flags%20will%20be%20handed%20out%20for%20%26quot%3Blimited%20onsite%20presence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20color%20by%20their%20name%20will%20be%20considered%20for%20performance%20evaluations%2C%20rewards%2C%20and%20compensation%2C%20Dell%20told%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaff%20who%20opted%20to%20remain%20remote%20during%20the%20company's%20overhaul%20of%20its%20hybrid%20work%20policy%2C%20which%20was%20first%20announced%20in%20February%2C%20will%20not%20be%20monitored.%20However%2C%20by%20choosing%20to%20stay%20remote%2C%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20eligible%20for%20promotion%20or%20able%20to%20change%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20employees%20who%20were%20classified%20as%20remote%20and%20hybrid%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20were%20disappointed%20with%20how%20the%20company%20was%20implementing%20this%20new%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDell%20is%20not%20the%20place%20it%20used%20to%20be%20where%20employees%20were%20respected%20and%20valued.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20people%20that%20are%20demoralized%20and%20will%20be%20hurt%20by%20this%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20Dell%20worker%2C%20who%20requested%20to%20remain%20anonymous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDell%20is%20in%20a%20state%20of%20dictatorship%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bde7da9-78f3-4e8b-8bf9-7359a1068b08%5C%22%3E'Lack%20of%20flexibility'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20staffers%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20flexibility%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20new%20monitoring%20system.%20One%20said%20that%20for%20a%20company%20dedicated%20to%20tech%20innovation%2C%20Dell's%20internal%20%26quot%3Btechnologies%20and%20approaches%20are%20totally%20outdated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20internal%20FAQ%20about%20the%20policy%20seen%20by%20BI%2C%20the%20attendance%20monitoring%20solution%20is%20solely%20based%20on%20data%20from%20badge%20swipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20if%20an%20employee%20forgets%20their%20badge%2C%20goes%20on%20a%20work%20trip%2C%20or%20takes%20an%20approved%20annual%20leave%2C%20the%20system%20marks%20them%20as%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAQ%20confirms%20that%20regularly%20turning%20up%20without%20a%20badge%20means%20you%20will%20show%20up%20as%20%26quot%3Bred%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dell%2C%20workers%20will%20not%20be%20penalized%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20Round%20Rock%20Texas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d765dbf533b039a885f016%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDell's%20HQ%20in%20Round%20Rock%20Texas%2C%20where%20staff%20attendance%20will%20be%20monitored.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20a%20way%20to%20systematically%20account%20for%20onsite%20attendance%20where%20no%20badge%20reader%20is%20available%2C%20so%20we%20will%20use%20the%20honor%20system%20and%20trust%20that%20you%20are%20adhering%20to%20the%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20told%20staff%20that%20by%20reporting%20attendance%20in%20ranges%2C%20the%20system%20can%20account%20for%20the%20odd%20%26quot%3Bdays%20that%20a%20team%20member%20has%20Dell-approved%20time%20off%2C%20business%20travel%2C%20corporate%20holidays%2C%20etc.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20what%20happens%20if%20an%20employee%20regularly%20falls%20out%20of%20a%20positive%20attendance%20bracket%20for%20legitimate%20reasons.%20This%20lack%20of%20clarity%20has%20caused%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20frustration%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20senior%20manager%20at%20Dell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20really%20knows%20what%20it%20means%20if%20you're%20designated%20hybrid%20but%20fail%20to%20meet%203%20days%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20BI%2C%20Dell%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20specific%20questions%20about%20the%20system's%20flexibility%20but%20confirmed%20that%20staff%20in%20hybrid%20roles%20were%20expected%20to%20be%20on-site%20at%20least%2039%20days%20per%20quarter%20%E2%80%94%20on%20average%2C%203%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20today's%20global%20technology%20revolution%2C%20we%20believe%20in-person%20connections%20paired%20with%20a%20flexible%20approach%20are%20critical%20to%20drive%20innovation%20and%20value%20differentiation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20is%20among%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20major%20corporations%20mandating%20more%20in-office%20work%20after%20years%20of%20working%20from%20home%20spurred%20by%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20initially%20embracing%20working%20from%20home%2C%20tech%20giants%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-making-workers-employees-return-to-office-rto-wfh-hybrid-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGoogle%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Salesforce%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20all%20moved%20away%20from%20remote%20work%20and%20now%20mandate%20employees%20spend%20a%20certain%20proportion%20of%20their%20time%20in%20the%20office.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20firms%20have%20faced%20an%20internal%20backlash%20over%20these%20policies.%20In%20February%2C%20financial%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeutsche-bank-staff-criticize-rto-mandate-not-enough-office-space-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeutsche%20Bank%20faced%20staff%20criticism%20after%20mandating%20three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office%20%3C%2Fa%3Edespite%20complaints%20that%20there%20wasn't%20enough%20space%20to%20house%20all%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225670ee24-9586-449f-8907-4ee180a90d92%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20hands%20of%20managers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20is%20placing%20responsibility%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-use-bossware-surveillance-track-workers-going-to-office-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etracking%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20individual%20managers%2C%20and%20any%20future%20action%20based%20on%20low%20attendance%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20at%20the%20leader's%20discretion%2C%20not%20driven%20centrally%20or%20by%20HR%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20FAQ%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20isn't%20as%20iron-fisted%20as%20it%20sounded%20when%20the%20announcement%20was%20first%20made%2C%20we%20can%20work%20with%20our%20management%20for%20abnormal%20exceptions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20employee%2C%20who%20%3Cspan%3Eviewed%20the%20manager-by-manager%20approach%20positively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20others%20see%20the%20new%20system%20as%20more%20work%20for%20already-stretched%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20an%20additional%20time%20sink%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20more%20keeps%20being%20pushed%20onto%20a%20smaller%20set%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20manager%20at%20Dell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leniency%20of%20managers%20will%20also%20differ%20across%20teams%2C%20BI's%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20staffer%20who%20works%20under%20senior%20management%20said%20their%20boss%20told%20staff%20that%20he%20will%20be%20satisfied%20as%20long%20