0the%20ability%20to%20work%20with%20your%20hands%2C%20blue-collar%20work%20is%20sexy.%20Look%20no%20further%20than%20the%20extremely%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40nenabebee%2Fvideo%2F7349283333798497567%3Fq%3Dblue%2520collar%2520boyfriend%26t%3D1711468858241%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikToks%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20bagging%20a%20blue-collar%20boyfriend%20or%20girlfriend.%20Or%20the%20people%20trying%20to%20find%20their%20next%20date%20on%20the%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20February%20there%20was%20a%20116%25%20increase%20in%20mentions%20of%20blue-collared%20jobs%20on%20OkCupid%20profiles%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20month%20last%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Kaye%2C%20the%20director%20of%20brand%20marketing%20and%20communications%20at%20OkCupid%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20an%20honest%20living%20is%20hot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Giambrone%20said%20that%20when%20he%20tells%20prospective%20matches%20on%20dating%20sites%20that%20he%20works%20at%20Walmart%2C%20they'll%20often%20unmatch%20or%20ghost%20him%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20how%20his%20friends%20and%20relatives%20see%20his%20work.%20But%20he%20knows%20that%20down%20the%20line%20he'll%20find%20his%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20make%20good%20money.%20I'm%20stable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20the%20fact%20that%20ultimately%20I%20work%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20a%20bed.%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20living%20somewhere.%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20food.%20I%20am%20comfortable.%20I%20live%20by%20myself.%20I%20have%20my%20two%20cats%2C%20and%20I'm%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGove%2C%20the%20UPS%20driver%2C%20said%20there's%20a%20long-running%20family%20joke%20about%20his%20relationship.%20%26quot%3BMy%20wife%20will%20tell%20you%20the%20reason%20she%20married%20me%20was%20for%20my%20healthcare%20benefits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp