Indian%20students%20who%20are%20planning%20to%20move%20abroad%20for%20higher%20education%20should%20not%20prioritise%20universities%20that%20have%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20Indian%20students.%20%26quot%3BAny%20Indian%20student%20planning%20to%20move%20abroad%20for%20higher%20education%20should%20check%20how%20many%20Indian%20students%20that%20university%20has.%20The%20more%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20students%2C%20the%20lower%20that%20university%20should%20be%20on%20your%20list%20of%20places%20to%20join%2C%26quot%3B%20Shreya%20Pattar%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20the%20reason%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20Founder%20of%20Shreya%20Pattar%20Ventures%2C%20said%20that%20the%20community%20%26quot%3Bcomes%20with%20toxic%20Indian%20patterns%26quot%3B%20which%20include%20%26quot%3Btoo%20much%20drama%2C%20lack%20of%20professionalism%2C%20no%20good%20role%20models%2C%20no%20leadership%20or%20responsibility%20towards%20juniors%2C%20self-centred%20behaviour%2C%20%26quot%3Bgroup-ism%26quot%3B%2C%20back%20bitching%2C%20no%20seriousness%20towards%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Pattar%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20plan%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20are%20also%20staying%20away%20from%20that%20mindset%2C%20attitude%2C%20and%20nature%20of%20people.%20You%20shouldn't%20need%20such%20people%20around%20you%20to%20'feel%20at%20home'.%20And%20if%20you%20DO%2C%20then%20might%20as%20well%20just%20not%20move%20abroad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAny%20Indian%20student%20planning%20to%20move%20abroad%20for%20higher%20education%20should%20check%20how%20many%20Indian%20students%20that%20university%20has.%20The%20more%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20students%2C%20the%20lower%20that%20university%20should%20be%20on%20your%20list%20of%20places%20to%20join.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20big%20Indian%20community%20of%20students%20doesn't%20come%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shreya%20Pattar%20(%40ShreyaPattar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShreyaPattar%2Fstatus%2F1789547977410785656%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20a%20over%20eight%20lakh%20views%20online.%20While%20many%20users%20agreed%20with%20her%2C%20some%20criticised%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTotally%20with%20you%20on%20this.%20The%20goal%20of%20studying%20abroad%20is%20to%20widen%20your%20horizons%20by%20interacting%20with%20diverse%20cultures%20and%20mindsets.%20Sticking%20to%20your%20comfort%20zone%20within%20a%20familiar%20community%20is%20counterproductive%20to%20that%20goal.%20It's%20about%20growing%20both%20personally%20and%20professionally%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20not%20agree%20more%20with%20you.%20In%202011%20I%20went%20to%20Australia%20to%20work%20in%20a%20hospital%20and%20there%20the%20most%20toxic%20people%20and%20most%20envious%20towards%20Indians%20were%20Indians%20only.%20It%20was%20a%20shock%20for%20me%20once%20I%20reach%20there%20and%20till%20the%20time%20I%20left%20Australia%20I%20could%20not%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20not%20want%20to%20hear%20this%2C%20but%20this%20is%20true!%20Having%20seen%20(and%20lived)%20this%20firsthand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20X%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20due%20respect%20this%20comes%20from%20your%20lack%20of%20exposure%20to%20other%20cultures%2C%20choice%20of%20your%20company%2C%20environment%20and%20upbringing%2C%20and%20myopic%20mindset.%20To%20get%20into%20a%20Canadian%20or%20American%20university%20means%20grinding%20work%20that%20leaves%20no%20time%20for%20what%20you're%20talking%20about.%20Your%20success%20will%20depend%20on%20your%20own%20individual%20efforts%20and%20not%20the%20ethnicity%20or%20background%20of%20other%20people%20enrolled%20in%20that%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20complaining%20another%20Indian%20about%20'Indians%20not%20good%20other%20Indians%2C'%20commented%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BSame%20goes%20for%20people%20from%20any%20country%20doing%20the%20same%20thing.%20Thank%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20respectfully%20disagree.%20Having%20a%20community%20of%20Indian%20students%20can%20provide%20a%20sense%20of%20familiarity%20and%20support%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20new%20country.%20It's%20about%20finding%20the%20right%20balance%20between%20comfort%20and%20exposure%20to%20diverse%20perspectives%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715760600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5h439kvg_graduation-generic_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Finfluencer-says-students-should-choose-universities-with-less-indians-sparks-debate-5667826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20a%20lot%20of%20reactions%20online.%20While%20many%20users%20agreed%20with%20her%2C%20some%20criticised%20her%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Finfluencer-says-students-should-choose-universities-with-less-indians-sparks-debate-5667826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Finfluencer-says-students-should-choose-universities-with-less-indians-sparks-debate-5667826%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Finfluencer-says-students-should-choose-universities-with-less-indians-sparks-debate-5667826%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20unleashes%20generative%20AI%20in%20Search%2C%20powered%20by