2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-contest-lok-sabha-polls-from-raebareli-announces-congress-5577052%5C%22%3ERahul%20filed%20his%20papers%20in%20Raebareli%3C%2Fa%3E%2012%20days%20back%2C%20it%20was%20an%20impromptu%2C%20dull%20event%2C%20devoid%20of%20even%20a%20roadshow.%20This%20was%20mostly%20because%20he%20had%20kept%20his%20candidature%20secret%20till%20about%203%20am%20on%20May%203%2C%20the%20logic%20being%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20the%20Raebareli%20nomination%20to%20affect%20his%20prospects%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%2C%20which%20voted%20on%20April%2026.%20The%20Election%20Commission's%20seven-phase%20poll%20schedule%20partly%20facilitated%20this%20dallying.%20INDIA%20bloc%20partners%20were%20mostly%20absent.%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20former%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20accompanied%20Rahul%2C%20as%20did%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20though%20that%20was%20because%20his%20state%20aircraft%20was%20needed%20to%20fly%20a%20few%20members%20of%20the%20entourage.%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20chief%20ministers%2C%20both%20of%20the%20Congress%20stock%2C%20were%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-why-did-rahul-choose-raebareli-over-amethi-5591461%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Why%20Did%20Rahul%20Choose%20Raebareli%20Over%20Amethi%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20was%20flanked%20by%20his%20family%20as%20he%20presented%20his%20papers.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20when%20Modi%20filed%20his%20nomination%2C%20by%20his%20side%20was%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20who%20does%20not%20have%20a%20family%20much%20like%20Modi%20himself.%20One%20of%20Modi's%20four%20proposers%20was%20Ganeshwar%20Shastri%20Dravid%2C%20a%20Tamil-origin%20Brahmin%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20based%20in%20Varanasi%20who%20had%20determined%20the%20%3Cem%3Emuhurat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(auspicious%20time)%20for%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%20%3Cem%3EPrana%20Pratishtha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eceremony.%20This%20had%20its%20own%20symbolism%20given%20Modi's%20outreach%20to%20Southern%20states%2C%20which%20saw%20a%20Sengol%20being%20installed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20last%20year%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Kashi-Tamil%20Sangamam%20that%20emphasised%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ancient%20links%20with%20Varanasi.%20Apart%20from%20Dravid%2C%20the%20other%20three%20proposers%20were%20Lalchand%20Kushwaha%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%20Sanjay%20Sonkar%2C%20a%20Dalit%2C%20and%20Baijnath%20Patel%2C%20a%20Brahmin%20-%20together%20reflecting%20the%20BJP's%20strong%20social%20engineering.%20Kushwaha%2C%20Sonkar%20and%20Patel%20are%20Panchayat-level%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20filing%20his%20papers%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20left%20Rae%20Bareli%20in%20a%20huff%2C%20avoiding%20the%20media%2C%20perhaps%20to%20fend%20off%20uncomfortable%20queries%20about%20not%20contesting%20from%20neighbouring%20Amethi.%20Modi%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20headed%20for%20a%20meeting%20with%20his%20party%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Ram%20Aur%20Kaam'%20vs%20'Karmabhoomi'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venue%20of%20this%20meeting%20was%20significant%20too.%20It%20was%20held%20at%20the%20state-of-the-art%20Rudraksh%20Convention%20Centre%2C%20a%20new%20landmark%20in%20Varanasi%20set%20up%20under%20Japanese%20collaboration%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20late%20Shinzo%20Abe%20had%20participated%20in%20the%20famous%20'Ganga%20Arati'%20in%20the%20city%20with%20Modi%20in%202015.%20The%20centre%20symbolises%20the%20transformation%20of%20Varanasi%20under%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20since%202014%2C%20and%20that%20transformation%20is%20being%20well%20highlighted%20in%20the%20pamphlets%20distributed%20by%20BJP%20workers.%20'%3Cem%3ERam%20aur%20Kaam%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(emphasis%20on%20religion%20as%20well%20as%20welfare)%20has%20become%20the%20favourite%20catchphrase%20for%20BJP%20%3Cem%3Evistaraks%20%3C%2Fem%3E(propagandists).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20Rahul's%20sister%20and%20principal%20campaigner%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20has%20been%20highlighting%20her%20family's%20century-old%20association%20with%20the%20region%20that%20goes%20back%20to%20Motilal%20Nehru's%20years%20as%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful.%20She%20has%20also%20been%20playing%20up%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20constituency%20has%20been%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fraebareli-amethi-not-just-constituencies-but-our-karmabhoomi-rahul-gandhi-5663264%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekarmabhoomi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E'%20(grandfather%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20won%20in%201952%20and%201957%20and%20created%20an%20abiding%20niche%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20a%20corruption-buster%20whose%20expos%C3%A9s%20made%20a%20finance%20minister%20resign%2C%20does%20not%20feature%20in%20the%20Congress%20discourse).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Interview%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20has%20held%20284%20roadshows%20so%20far%20for%20this%20year's%20election%20and%20has%20given%2031%20television%20interviews%20in%20recent%20days.%20In%20one%20of%20those%20interviews%2C%20conducted%20soon%20after%20he%20filed%20his%20nomination%2C%20PM%20Modi%2C%20upon%20being%20questioned%20about%20his%20criticism%20of%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-cant-think-beyond-dynasty-corruption-and-appeasement-pm-modi-5118216%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eparivarvaad%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E'%20(dynastic%20politics)%2C%20said%20that%20his%20kinship%20extends%20to%20all%20140%20crore%20Indians%2C%20and%20that%20unlike%20many%20who%20treat%20supporters%20as%20'%3Cem%3Ejanata%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(public)%20or%20'%3Cem%3Esevak%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(workers)%2C%20he%20prefers%20to%20see%20them%20as%20family.%20To%20accusations%20that%20he%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bautocrat%26quot%3B%2C%20Modi%20said%20it%20was%20an%20abuse%20hurled%20at%20not%20him%20but%20the%20voters%20who%20have%20given%20him%20two%20mandates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20the%20charge%20that%20he%20would%20alter%20the%20Constitution%20if%20he%20is%20re-elected%2C%20Modi%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20First%20Amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%20was%20brought%20about%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20in%201951%20through%20the%20Provisional%20Parliament%20that%20had%20only%20limited%20franchise%3B%20the%20first%20Lok%20Sabha%20under%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20was%20elected%20in%201952%2C%20which%20made%20changes%20to%20the%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20and%20expression%20(the%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20said%20it%20may%20consider%20a%20PIL%20to%20examine%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20First%20Amendment).%20He%20further%20referred%20to%20the%20imposition%20of%20Emergency%20in%201975%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20cited%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20regime's%20legislation%20to%20overturn%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20Shah%20Bano%20verdict%20as%20yet%20another%20Congress-era%20constitutional%20oddity%20that%20ultimately%20resulted%20in%20the%20denial%20of%20rights%20to%20Muslim%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhen-indira-gandhi-died-pm-modi-on-why-rajiv-gandhi-ended-inheritance-tax-5521569%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BWhen%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Died...%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20Why%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Ended%20Inheritance%20Tax%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20recalled%20how%20in%202013%2C%20Rahul%20tore%20up%20an%20ordinance%20that%20sought%20to%20provide%20a%20safety%20net%20for%20convicted%20legislators.%20The%20ordinance%20had%20been%20passed%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Cabinet%2C%20a%20duly%20recognised%20constitutional%20body%2C%20and%20was%20signed%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20the%20highest%20constitutional%20authority.%20Modi%20asked%20whether%20that%20was%20not%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20constitution.%20Notably%2C%20Rahul's%20act%2C%20perhaps%20intended%20to%20announce%20his%20arrival%20as%20the%20new%20Congress%20boss%2C%20had%20come%20barely%20a%20few%20hours%20ahead%20of%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20White%20House%20meeting%20with%20the%20then%20US%20President%2C%20Barack%20Obama.%20The%20Congress%20government%20was%20defied%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20on%20a%20state%20visit%20abroad.%20The%20irony%20is%20that%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20Rahul's%20own%20brashness%20came%20back%20to%20haunt%20him%20when%20he%20was%20convicted%20for%20defamation%20by%20a%20Surat%20court%20last%20year%2C%20with%20no%20legal%20protection%20to%20cushion%20the%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrince%20vs%20Emperor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20insists%20on%20calling%20Rahul%20a%20%26quot%3BShahzada%26quot%3B%20(Prince).%20Priyanka%20has%20countered%20this%20by%20calling%20Modi%20a%20%26quot%3BShehenshah%26quot%3B%20(Emperor).%20Before%20embarking%20for%20Varanasi%20on%20May%2013%2C%20Modi%20replied%20to%20her%20through%20an%20interview%20in%20Patna%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMujhe%20saalon%20se%20gaaliyan%20padti%20rahi%20hain%2C%20main%20sab%20seh%20leta%20hoon.%20Shayad%20meri%20sahansheelta%20ke%20karan%20mujhe%20sehenshah%20kaha%20gaya%20ho%20%3C%2Fem%3E(I%20have%20been%20tolerating%20abuse%20for%20years.%20Perhaps%20my%20tolerance%20-%C2%A0%3Cem%3Esahansheelta%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E-%20has%20invited%20this%20epithet).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20filing%20his%20papers%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20Rahul%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Priyanka%20and%20her%20husband%20Robert%20Vadra%2C%20was%20photographed%20offering%20prayers%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20priest%20who%20has%20been%20conducting%20pre-nomination%20ceremonies%20for%20the%20family%20since%20the%20days%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20The%20three%20sat%20on%20stools.%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20used%20to%20sit%20cross-legged%20on%20the%20floor%20as%20per%20conventional%20Hindu%20tradition.%20Modi%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20did%20Ganga%20Arati%20on%20May%2013%2C%20prayed%20at%20designated%20temples%20in%20traditional%20style%2C%20and%20then%20proceeded%20to%20file%20his%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20gesture%2C%20Modi%20and%20Rahul%20stood%20worlds%20apart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715758260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F6387g7j_pm-modi-rahul-gandhi-650-_650x400_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnarendra-modi-and-rahul-gandhi-in-uttar-pradesh-two-nominations-worlds-apart-5667477%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Personae%20and%20political%20styles%20came%20into%20sharp%20relief%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20filed%20their%20nominations%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20two%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20seats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnarendra-modi-and-rahul-gandhi-in-uttar-pradesh-two-nominations-worlds-apart-5667477%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20killed%20in%20New%20Caledonia%20as%20riots%20escalate%20after%20Paris%20vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715758233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F75d1%2Flive%2Ffda88ec0-1284-11ef-9654-bfcbf4a287a1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1d4dlxd10xo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20riots%20come%20in%20response%20to%20the%20French%20parliament%20giving%20French%20residents%20there%20more%20voting%20rights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1d4dlxd10xo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1d4dlxd10xo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1d4dlxd10xo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Ponting%2C%20Fleming%20on%20BCCI's%20radar%20for%20India%20head%20coach%20job'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715758228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110141126%2Cimgsize-79260.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fricky-ponting-stephen-fleming-on-bccis-radar-for-india-head-coach-job-report%2Farticleshow%2F110140698.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20head%20coach%20race%20has%20accelerated%20due%20to%20incumbent%20Rahul%20Dravid's%20reluctance%20to%20continue.%20The%20BCCI%20is%20considering%20foreign%20coaches%20like%20Stephen%20Fleming%20and%20Ricky%20Ponting%2C%20for%20their%20extensive%20knowledge%20of%20Indian%20cricket.%20However%2C%20the%20year-round%20commitment%20presents%20a%20potential%20deterrent%2C%20with%20Fleming%20and%20Ponting%20showing%20lukewarm%20responses%20as%20per%20sources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fricky-ponting-stephen-fleming-on-bccis-radar-for-india-head-coach-job-report%2Farticleshow%2F110140698.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trial%20Reveals%20Creepy%20Details%20Of%20How%20Indian-Origin%20Man%20Stole%20Intimate%20Photos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian-origin%20man%2C%20employed%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Air%20Force%2C%20was%20on%20Wednesday%20sentenced%20to%2011%20months%20in%20jail%20for%20phishing%20women's%20social%20media%20login%20details%20to%20get%20their%20intimate%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Eshwaran%2C%2026%2C%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%2010%20charges%20under%20the%20Computer%20Misuse%20Act.%20Another%2021%20charges%20were%20considered%20for%20sentencing%2C%20Channel%20News%20Asia%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202019%20to%202023%2C%20he%20sent%20phishing%20links%20to%2022%20victims%20to%20get%20login%20credentials%20for%20their%20social%20media%2C%20cloud%20server%20and%20email%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEshwaran%20targeted%20victims%20whom%20he%20knew%20in%20real%20life%20or%20victims%20whose%20intimate%20images%20had%20been%20posted%20to%20an%20adult%20forum%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20identities%20of%20all%20his%20victims%20were%20protected%20by%20a%20court%20order%2C%20which%20the%20prosecution%20requested%20given%20the%20sexual%20element%20of%20his%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPosing%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhelpful%20netizen%26quot%3B%2C%20Eshwaran%20would%20send%20phishing%20links%20to%20victims%20with%20a%20message%20saying%20that%20their%20intimate%20images%20had%20been%20posted%20online%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20he%20used%20a%20website%20to%20generate%20possible%20login%20credentials%20based%20on%20a%20victim's%20social%20media%20details%20that%20he%20had%20and%20then%20used%20trial%20and%20error%20to%20access%20their%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20inside%20the%20accounts%2C%20he%20would%20trawl%20through%20them%20to%20see%20if%20the%20victims%20had%20stored%20any%20intimate%20images%20of%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20one%20victim%2C%20Eshwaran%20knew%20she%20had%20done%20modelling%20shoots%20where%20she%20was%20partially%20dressed%20or%20in%20lingerie%2C%20and%20wanted%20access%20to%20those%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20once%2C%20he%20also%20gained%20unauthorised%20access%20to%20men's%20social%20media%20accounts.%20He%20would%20then%20impersonate%20the%20account%20holder%20and%20contact%20women%20whom%20he%20thought%20had%20an%20intimate%20relationship%20with%20the%20man%20to%20ask%20for%20intimate%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEshwaran%20continued%20to%20re-offend%20in%202023%2C%20even%20when%20he%20was%20out%20on%20bail%20and%20already%20under%20investigation%20for%20his%20earlier%20phishing%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20that%20year%2C%20he%20gained%20unauthorised%20access%20to%20the%20Instagram%20and%20Snapchat%20accounts%20of%20his%20victim%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20her%20early%2020s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20finding%20her%20intimate%20images%20in%20her%20Snapchat%20account%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20send%20her%20phishing%20links%20to%20gain%20login%20credentials%20to%20her%20other%20online%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20and%20other%20cases%2C%20the%20internet%20protocol%20address%20used%20in%20the%20unauthorised%20access%20of%20the%20accounts%20was%20traced%20to%20Eshwaran's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20victims%20also%20made%20police%20reports%20after%20realising%20they%20were%20being%20phished%20or%20that%20their%20accounts%20had%20been%20hacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20sought%2011%20to%2016%20months%20of%20jail%20time.%20Deputy%20Public%20Prosecutor%20Joshua%20Phang%20argued%20that%20Eshwaran's%20offences%20were%20premeditated%20and%20sophisticated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20lawyer%20Mervyn%20Tan%20said%20that%20Eshwaran%20was%20a%20first-time%20offender%20and%20that%20his%20crimes%20were%20%26quot%3Ban%20act%20of%20mischief%2C%20malicious%20though%20it%20may%20be%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20court%20that%20Eshwaran%20was%20a%20regular%20serving%20as%20an%20engineer%20in%20the%20Republic%20of%20Singapore%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETan%20said%20Eshwaran%20was%20likely%20to%20suffer%20professional%20consequences%20as%20a%20result%20of%20his%20offences%2C%20and%20asked%20District%20Judge%20Wong%20Peck%20to%20take%20this%20into%20account%20as%20a%20mitigating%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Eshwaran's%20family%20had%20%26quot%3Bcome%20together%26quot%3B%20after%20his%20offences%20and%20that%20his%20parents%20had%20%26quot%3Btaken%20him%20to%20task%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20agreed%20with%20the%20prosecution's%20sentencing%20position%20and%20said%20there%20were%20far%20more%20aggravating%20than%20mitigating%20factors%20in%20Eshwaran's%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEshwaran%20will%20start%20serving%20his%20sentence%20on%20June%2019%20after%20the%20judge%20granted%20his%20request%20for%20a%20deferral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETan%20told%20the%20court%20that%20Eshwaran's%20wife%20had%20just%20given%20birth%20in%20early%20May%2C%20and%20he%20needed%20the%20time%20to%20settle%20personal%20matters%20and%20help%20her%20with%20confinement.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715758200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Ftmcj0cnk_pornography-generic_625x300_29_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Ftrial-reveals-creepy-details-of-how-indian-origin-man-stole-intimate-photos-5667378%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-origin%20man%2C%20employed%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Air%20Force%2C%20was%20on%20Wednesday%20sentenced%20to%2011%20months%20in%20jail%20for%20phishing%20women's%20social%20media%20login%20details%20to%20get%20their%20intimate%20images.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Ftrial-reveals-creepy-details-of-how-indian-origin-man-stole-intimate-photos-5667378%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Ftrial-reveals-creepy-details-of-how-indian-origin-man-stole-intimate-photo