radh%2C%20a%20city%20known%20for%20its%20oil%20and%20gas%20reserves%2C%20to%20Al%20Batha%2C%20near%20the%20border%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fworld-records%2F62919-longest-straight-road%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGuinness%20World%20Records%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eit%20cuts%20through%20the%20desert%20with%20no%20bends%20left%20or%20right%20or%20any%20appreciable%20gradient%20up%20or%20down.%20The%20super-straight%20stretch%20has%20an%20estimated%20driving%20time%20of%20around%202%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20Eyre%20Highway%2C%20a%20146-kilometre-long%20stretch%20connecting%20Western%20Australia%20and%20South%20Australia%2C%20held%20the%20record%20for%20the%20straightest%20road.%20While%20driving%20on%20Highway%2010%20might%20seem%20like%20setting%20the%20cruise%20control%20on%20autopilot%2C%20drivers%20are%20warned%20against%20complacency.%20Information%20found%20on%20dangerousroads.org%20emphasises%20that%2C%20despite%20the%20lack%20of%20bends%2C%20collisions%20are%20not%20uncommon.%20The%20desert%20landscape%20presents%20its%20own%20set%20of%20hazards%2C%20with%20vehicles%20needing%20to%20be%20cautious%20of%20stray%20camels%20and%20the%20occasional%20kangaroo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20reasons%20behind%20building%20such%20a%20long%2C%20straight%20road%20remain%20unknown%2C%20some%20speculate%20it%20served%20as%20a%20high-speed%20route%20for%20the%20King.%20Regardless%20of%20its%20origin%2C%20Highway%2010%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20modern%20engineering%20and%20a%20truly%20unique%20driving%20experience%2C%20albeit%20one%20that%20requires%20a%20healthy%20dose%20of%20driver%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715757480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fsks8bpo_saudi-arabias-highway-10_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhighway