F73988%2Fantioxidant-rich-foods-combat-pollution-stress%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantioxidant%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E%20possessed%20by%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20roots%2C%20stems%20and%20leaves%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20golden%20foliage.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20there%20are%20800%20Patwa%20plants%20that%20are%20thriving%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaturvedi%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIllegal%20trade%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20contributing%20factor%20to%20the%20slow%20death%20of%20this%20miracle%20plant.%20Highlighting%20the%20problem%2C%20Chaturvedi%20says%2C%20the%20plant%20habitats%20bordering%20Tibet%20and%20Nepal%20lead%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20cases.%20But%20even%20as%20he%20adds%20that%20cracking%20down%20on%20these%20cases%20lies%20beyond%20his%20jurisdiction%2C%20he%20is%20reminded%20of%20a%20childhood%20anecdote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20shorten%20an%20existing%20line%2C%20just%20draw%20a%20bigger%20line%20next%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20Chaturvedi%20learnt%20early%20on%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20plant%20species%20of%20Uttarakhand%20thrived%20despite%20all%20odds%20was%20to%20ensure%20their%20propagation%20was%20amped%20up.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20day%20one%2C%20we%20have%20made%20it%20our%20motto%20that%20if%20there%20are%20100%20plants%20in%20the%20initial%20habitat%2C%20we%20will%20grow%20500%20in%20our%20centres.%E2%80%9D%20Currently%2C%202%2C200%20endemic%20plant%20species%20are%20being%20conserved%20across%20the%20forest%20wing%E2%80%99s%20seven%20centres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-2-1715250601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Tamil%20Palm%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20species%20that%20can%20survive%