20was%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20would%20want%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20aerospace.%20But%20how%2C%20where%2C%20and%20what%20to%20do%20to%20achieve%20this%20dream%20was%20a%20path%20she%20had%20to%20navigate%20on%20her%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20incredible%20talent%20and%20a%20dogged%20pursuit%20of%20her%20goal%2C%20she%20became%20a%20student%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%2C%20which%20was%20a%20huge%20deal%20for%20the%20student%20who%20studied%20in%20a%20state%20board%20school%20and%20came%20from%20a%20middle%20class%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20this%20gritty%20woman%20works%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaerospace%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration%20(NASA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20her%20journey%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavigating%20through%20the%20various%20hurdles%20of%20having%20an%20education%20abroad%20to%20setting%20foot%20at%20NASA%20as%20a%20full-time%20employee%20took%20her%20almost%2015%20years.%20But%20this%2035-year-old%20is%20making%20it%20easy%20for%20others%20by%20sharing%20her%20experiences%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20mentoring%20them.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20her%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIn%20pursuit%20of%20the%20universe%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshata%20works%20as%20a%20Principal%20Investigator%20and%20Space%20Systems%20Engineer%20at%20NASA%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%20(JPL)%20on%20two%20space%20missions.%20She%20is%20the%20mission%20science%20phase%20lead%20on%20the%20NASA-ISRO%20Synthetic%20Aperture%20Radar%20mission%20(NISAR)%20and%20robotics%20systems%20engineer%20on%20the%20MARS%202020%20Pers