edia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPathshala%20started%20as%20a%20mobile%20teaching%20initiative%20before%20Juin%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20residential%20school.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20to%20their%20efforts%20was%20good%2C%20so%20the%20group%20divided%20their%20efforts%20and%20started%20to%20teach%20in%20three%20different%20locations%20in%20Vadodara.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20some%20months%2C%20from%20a%20dozen%20kids%2C%20we%20went%20to%20teaching%20hundreds.%20But%20the%20problem%20was%20that%20every%20six%20months%2C%20these%20workers%20would%20move%20and%20hence%20the%20kids%20would%20be%20left%20with%20no%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20mothers%20who%20requested%20Juin%20to%20take%20her%20child%20under%20her%20wing%20and%20provide%20education%20as%20they%20were%20to%20migrate%20once%20more.%20Inspired%20by%20it%2C%20in%202014%2C%20Juin%20decided%20to%20resign%20from%20her%20job%20and%20dedicate%20herself%20to%20assisting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F100208%2Fsnehlata-hooda-teaching-underprivileged-children-in-gurugram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20children.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20hostel%20was%20born.%20A%20very%20kind%20philanthropist%20from%20the%20city%20helped%20us%20to%20get%20a%20property%20for%20rent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20free%20residential%20school%20operates%2C%20unlike%20traditional%20institutions%2C%20employing%20a%20unique%20educational%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20Juin%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20diverse%20backgrounds%20of%20our%20students%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20commence%20their%20education%20later%20in%20life%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20adopted%20a%20levelled%20system%20of%20instruction.%20In%20our%20approach%2C%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20level%20in%20a%20particular%20subject%20is%20determined%20by%20their%20proficiency%20rather%20than%20their%20age%2C%20ensuring%20no%20one%20feels%20misplaced%20or%20ashamed%20for%20joining%20later.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20prioritise%20sports%20and%20project-based%20activities%2C%20offering%20opportunities%20for%20learning%20beyond%20the%20conventional%20curriculum%2C%20such%20as%20painting%2C%20judo%2C%20and%20karate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuin%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20how%20a%20student%20is%20assigned%20a%20particular%20lever%20and%20how%20they%20navigate%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20joins%20Pathshala%2C%20we%20assess%20their%20current%20knowledge%20and%20comprehension%20abilities%20in%20languages%20and%20mathematics.%20Based%20on%20this%20evaluation%2C%20we%20place%20them%20in%20appropriate%20levels%20corresponding%20to%20their%20proficiency.%20Consequently%2C%20each%20child%20studies%20at%20different%20levels%20for%20various%20subjects.%20Upon%20completion%20of%20Level%205%2C%20a%20student%20becomes%20equivalent%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20sit%20for%20Class%208%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Class%208%20to%2012%2C%20the%20school%20adheres%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS)%20syllabus%2C%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20take%20psychometric%20tests%20to%20discover%20their%20career%20inclinations%2C%20guiding%20their%20subject%20choices%20when%20they%20enter%20Class%208.%20This%20personalised%20method%20ensures%20their%20interests%20and%20strengths%20are%20considered.%20Alongside%20languages%20and%20math%2C%20students%20explore%20diverse%20subjects%20through%20practical%20experiences%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20recently%2C%20the%20students%20completed%20a%20board%20game%20project%20where%20they%20designed%20and%20created%20their%20own%20board%20games%2C%20complete%20with%20unique%20rules.%20Students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20delve%20deeply%20into%20subjects%20of%20their%20choosing%20and%20conduct%20in-depth%20studies%20according%20to%20their%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children's%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmeen%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20living%20in%20Pathshala%20hostel%20and%20has%20been%20with%20Juin%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20shares%20his%20perspective%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20enriching%20aspect%20of%20our%20education%20is%20a%20class%20where%20we%20learn%20without%20textbooks.%20We%20select%20a%20topic%2C%20discuss%20it%2C%20and%20learn%20from%20each%20other%20and%20our%20teachers.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20educators%20stress%20on%20understanding%20concepts%20deeply%20rather%20than%20just%20memorisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20second%20chance%20at%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20these%20kids%20have%20a%20safe%20place%20here%20to%20thrive%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20their%20lives%20still%20lingers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jui.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20hail%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20travel%20frequently%2C%20leaving%20their%20children%20under%20my%20care.%20Yet%2C%20upon%20returning%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20these%20children%20confront%20challenges%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20face%20at%20such%20tender%20ages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20a%20distressing%20incident%20during%20their%20summer%20vacation%20when%20she%20encountered%20one%20of%20her%20students%20begging%20on%20the%20streets.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20children%20who%20stay%20with%20us%20leave%20for%20summer%20vacations%20to%20their%20homes.%20While%20we%20try%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20life%20here%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20poverty%20they%20were%20born%20into%20hits%20hard.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20these%20vacation%20days%20that%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20students%20begging.%20It%20was%20heart-wrenching%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20upset.%20I%20spoke%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20but%20the%20mother%20simply%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98How%20will%20they%20eat%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20beg%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20Juin%20realised%20the%20stark%20contrast%20the%20children%20experience%20in%20their%20transition%20from%20hostel%20to%20home.%20It%20stressed%20the%20gravity%20of%20her%20work%2C%20as%20it%20dawned%20upon%20her%20that%20good%20education%20serves%20as%20their%20only%20ticket%20to%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20reflecting%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20hunger%2C%20Juin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20young%20boy%20under%20our%20care%20who%20confessed%20that%20chewing%20%3Cem%3Egutka%3C%2Fem%3E%20(tobacco)%20helped%20curb%20his%20hunger.%20That%20statement%20shattered%20me.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20begin%20to%20comprehend%20the%20mental%20anguish%20that%20boy%20endured.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20what%20the%20foundation%20aims%20to%20fight.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20about%20educating%20them%20but%20also%20making%20them%20independent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuin%20explains%20that%20once%20the%20children%20are%20prepared%20to%20leave%20Pathshala%2C%20she%20assists%20them%20in%20acquiring%20vocational%20education%20to%20secure%20employment%20or%20gain%20admission%20to%20college%20for%20further%20education.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20only%20way%20we%20can%20ensure%20that%20these%20children%20have%20a%20good%20life%20not%20just%20at%20the%20hostel%20but%20beyond%20it%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Juin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-wid