of%20Vegan%20Ice%20Creams%E2%80%99%20store%20in%20Trichy%20in%202020.%20The%20flavours%20they%20offer%20range%20from%20vanilla%2C%20chocolate%2C%20mango%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20and%20jamun%2C%20to%20red%20guava%2C%20dates%2C%20banana%2C%20musk%20melon%2C%20strawberry%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20coconut%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20vegan%20ice%20creams%2C%20millet%20milk%20is%20subtle%20and%20does%20not%20dominate%20other%20flavours.%20We%20use%20different%20sweeteners%20in%20different%20ice%20creams%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20fruits%20being%20used.%20For%20example%2C%20jaggery%20works%20well%20with%20some%20fruits%2C%20while%20palm%20sugar%20works%20better%20with%20some.%20It%20also%20varies%20depending%20on%20the%20millet%20being%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Prabu%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20also%20sell%20shakes%2C%20waffles%2C%20brownies%2C%20and%20other%20products%20in%20their%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20scoop%20of%20ice%20cream%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2030%2C%20and%20a%20one-litre%20pack%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%20800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20factory%20in%20Trichy%20has%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349601%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20factory%20in%20Trichy%20has%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20that%2C%20they%20also%20realised%20that%20these%20nutritious%20ice%20creams%20are%20a%20good%20way%20to%20introduce%20children%20to%20millets%20and%20get%20them%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20this%20traditional%20Indian%20grain!%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20think%20of%20millets%20as%20a%20punishment.%20Research%20shows%20that%20kids%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267083%2Fpapacream-woman-entrepreneur-vegan-ice-cream-engineer-quits-job-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eice%20creams%20and%20shakes%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%2C%20this%20would%20be%20a%20good%20mode%20to%20introduce%20them%20to%20these%20powerhouses%20of%20nutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20millets%20are%20procured%20from%20their%20own%20farms%2C%20and%20other%20farmers%20in%20Theni%2C%20Dharmapuri%2C%20and%20Krishnagiri%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20is%20entirely%20self-funded%2C%20with%20each%20of%20the%20four%20founders%20investing%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20their%20savings%20into%20realising%20their%20dream.%20Their%20most%20significant%20hurdle%20post-launch%20has%20been%20the%20widespread%20lack%20of%20awareness%20surrounding%20millets.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20diligently%20engaged%20in%20consumer%20education%20initiatives%2C%20conducting%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20create%20customer%20awareness.%20We%20started%20visiting%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20educate%20the%20youth%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20nutritious%20eating%20habits.%20We%20believe%20that%20knowledge%20is%20the%20key%20to%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20take%20students%20on%20a%20factory%20tour%20to%20show%20them%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20In%202023%2C%20they%20established%20a%20factory%20in%20Trichy%2C%20with%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20opened%20outlets%20in%20Hyderabad%20near%20the%20Statue%20of%20Equality%20and%20one%20in%20Rajahmundry.%20They%20are%20poised%20to%20launch%2010%20to%2012%20more%20outlets%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20community%20engagement%20is%20equally%20important.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20treasures%20of%20our%20ancestors%2C%20adapted%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20is%20seeing%20an%20increasing%20shift%20towards%20millets%2C%20this%20is%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20include%20them%20in%20our%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Prabu%20Venugopal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715180752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F%40Siri-Millet-Ice-Creams-52-of-64-min-1715319230.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prabu%20Venugopal%2C%20Shashidhar%2C%20Arun%20Prakash%2C%20and%20Bhargav%20left%20their%20comfortable%20careers%20to%20introduce%20a%20healthy%2C%20vegan%20ice%20cream%20alternative%20made%20using%20millets.%20They%20founded%20Siri%20Millet%20Ice%20Creams%20in%20Trichy%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20are%20actively%20healthy%20eating%20habits%20through%20educational%20initiatives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349369%2Fsiri-millet-vegan-ice-cream-trichy-non-dairy-healthy-frozen-dessert%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Meet%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Sumeet%20Saigal%2C%20Whose%20Pani%20Puri%20Took%20MasterChef%20Australia%20By%20Storm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20come%20up%20with%20the%20recipe%20for%20a%20diabetic%20biscuit%E2%80%A6something%20diabetics%20can%20eat%20guilt-free%2C%E2%80%9D%20S%20Jagjit%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20freedom%20fighter%20and%20an%20intrinsic%20part%20of%20the%20independence%20movement%20since%201930%2C%20once%20told%20his%20granddaughter%20Sumeet%20Saigal%20over%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20duo%20treasured%20these%20sessions%20where%20they%20spoke%20about%20everything%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20particularly%20food-forward%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20conversation%20was%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Singh%20toyed%20with%20the%20brilliant%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F223780%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-harsh-kedia-diabetic-chef-guilt-free-desserts-inspiring-india-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediabetic-friendly%20biscuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rarity%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20his%20grandaughter%20was%20amazed.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20you%20know%20where%20I%20get%20it%20from%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles%2C%20referring%20to%20her%20passion%20for%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MasterChef%20Australia%20Season%2016%20contestant%20may%20have%20traversed%20the%20world%2C%20but%20all%20roads%20have%20always%20led%20back%20home%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20household%20that%20witnessed%20a%20confluence%20of%20culture%20as%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20Punjabi%20descent%20and%20love%20for%20%3Cem%3Erajma%20chawal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(red%20kidney%20beans%20in%20a%20thick%20gravy%20served%20with%20rice)%20blended%20with%20their%20occasional%20preference%20for%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20crepe%20made%20with%20fermented%20batter)%20and%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20savoury%20condiment).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20powerhouse%20of%20flavour%20that%20Saigal%20has%20been%20bringing%20to%20the%20MasterChef%20table%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20season.%20And%20her%20culinary%20prowess%20has%20been%20winning%20both%20palettes%20and%20hearts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20settles%20down%20for%20a%20t%C3%AAte-%C3%A0-t%C3%AAte%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20where%20she%20shares%20the%20reciprocal%20relationship%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20always%20shared%20with%20food%2C%20traces%20her%20steps%20back%20to%20the%20biggest%20influences%20in%20her%20life%2C%20and%20elaborates%20on%20how%20the%20dots%20connected%20to%20lead%20her%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292787%2Fmasterchef-australia-sandeep-pandit-revives-traditional-kashmiri-pandit-recipes-indian-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld%E2%80%99s%20most%20coveted%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99d%20say%20my%20paternal%20grandfather%20impacted%20my%20love%20for%20food%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20His%20ideas%20were%20almost%20like%20mind-benders%20for%20me.%20They%20caused%20me%20to%20think%20beyond%20the%20obvious.%E2%80%9D%20An%20anecdote%20that%20sums%20up%20her%20%3Cem%3Edarji%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20out-of-the-box%20thinking%20is%20when%20on%20a%20shopping%20spree%20he%20picked%20up%20a%20bottle%20of%20ketchup%2C%20took%20a%20good%20look%20at%20the%20ingredients%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Oh%2C%20we%20can%20make%20this%20at%20home!%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20his%20word%2C%20he%20spent%20the%20next%20many%20hours%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20experimenting%20to%20get%20the%20flavours%20right.%20And%20the%20result%20was%20pretty%20good%2C%20Saigal%20affirms.%20When%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20prodding%20her%20to%20think%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20the%20ordinary%2C%20he%20was%20researching%20recipes%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%20And%20as%20grandfather%20and%20granddaughter%20sat%20down%20to%20dissect%20these%2C%20fascination%20flooded%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20was%20amazed%20at%20his%20thirst%20for%20knowledge%20and%20his%20hunger%20made%20me%20hungry%20to%20learn%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reminisces.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229381%2Fzero-waste-how-to-cook-cooking-tips-traditional-indian-food-using-leftovers-mother-grandmother-recipes-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAstounding%20cooking%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20run%20in%20the%20family%20DNA%3B%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20stories%20reveal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20of%20restaurants%20in%20India%20helmed%20by%20her%20extended%20family%20are%20a%20testament%20to%20this%20%E2%80%94%20The%20Great%20Punjab%20restaurant%2C%20Hotel%20Diplomat%20(adjacent%20to%20the%20iconic%20Taj%20Palace%20Hotel)%2C%20Jashan%20restaurant%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Sher-e-Punjab%20in%20Pune.%20Through%20these%20ventures%2C%20the%20family%20has%20been%20delighting%20generations%20with%20their%20food%20and%20flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20performance%20in%20the%20MasterChef%20kitchen%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20this.%20But%20the%20journey%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Australia%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20without%20its%20detours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeepers%20of%20tradition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20ardent%20fan%20of%20the%20cooking%20show%20MasterChef%20Australia%20wat