0microgreens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20am%20at%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20market%20or%20at%20pop-ups%20and%20am%20interacting%20with%20the%20people%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20unawareness%20among%20them.%20Including%20these%20little%20pockets%20of%20nutrition%20in%20your%20daily%20diet%20can%20really%20do%20wonders%20for%20your%20body.%20They%20contain%20large%20amounts%20of%20vitamins%20B%2C%20K%20and%20C%2C%20folic%20acid%2C%20magnesium%2C%20minerals%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20which%20have%20immense%20health%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20consume%2020-30%20gm%20of%20a%20microgreen%20vegetable%2C%20you%20are%20eating%20double%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20regular%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22She%20grows%20and%20sells%2050%20kgs%20of%20microgreens%20every%20month.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349307%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20grows%20and%20sells%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20every%20month.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3